race.comment: DEEP EMOTION (9) sharp improver when she launched late from last on the turn with a tenacious win over 1300m at Kembla Grange. Confidence is high and looks up to this stiffer contest with fitness on her side. XCESSIVE FORCE (4) lightly raced mare with a ton of upside. Resumes after she gripped on late in the heavy (10) going when second over 1100m at Randwick in Highway grade last August. Undefeated in two starts here and expected to go close. ICONIC TREASURE (1) frustrating the stable this time in and gets one more chance at this level. Went back from the draw and never comfortable in the heavy (8) conditions when ninth over 1200m at Rosehill in Midway grade. Claim helps and ready to produce. GOOFINATOR (3) staying gelding resuming. Created a big impression at his last start when a commanding 4.5 len win over 3200m at Wagga last October. Placed in a recent 1000m trial at Wagga. Look for him doing his best work late.
